attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Rare opportunity to own a detached single-family brick home with a large backyard in South Boston! Recently renovated with designer touches, this property features high ceilings, custom built-ins and modern elegance throughout. On the main floor is a state-of-the-art kitchen with stainless steel appliances, 36" Italian range, quartz countertops, herringbone floors and ample cabinetry that seamlessly flows into the bright, airy living and dining areas--ideal for entertaining. Upstairs, a luxurious spa bathroom offers a soaking tub and sleek finishes. Four bedrooms provide versatile space for guests, home offices, or nurseries. The professionally designed and landscaped yard is your own private urban oasis for relaxing or gathering. The basement provides plentiful storage, laundry room and workout area. Blocks from the beach, public transit, shops, restaurants and new developments, this exceptional home offers the best of city living and a chance to own a classic piece of Boston history.

exclusions: Dining Area And Front Bedroom Light Fixtures (Total Of 2)
